<a href="/mobile/articles/12535.html" class="com-grid-key-article">
	<div class="grid-key-article-hd">
		<div class="imgcover">
				<img class="pic" src="/system/articles/banners/12535/medium/12535.jpg?1437646779" alt="如果有些新闻素材跟电影一样，如何把它们拍成真的电影？">
